page.title: 01E WORTHING,SOMPTING,LANCING
page.content: The area covered by our block is a mixture of residential,commercial, industrial and agricultural useage. It takes in parts of East Worthing Sompting and Lancing,all situated along the south coast of West Susse. Worthing has its own Borough Council where as Sompting and Lancing form part of the Adur District.The Residential parts dominate the are, but there are some quite sizeable shoping/commercial areas an important industrial estate and two small agricultural areas with two farms. There are good road and rail communications through the area and the beach,which runs the length of the block is a mixture of shingle and sand.
